details: Description: Introducing Baby Stella, the perfect first baby doll for young children. This soft and cuddly doll has a lifelike appearance.

The JC Toys La Baby Doll is a lifelike baby doll that's perfect for nurturing play. It has a realistic facial expression, soft body, and movable arms, legs, and head.

The Barbie Fashionista Doll is part of the diverse and inclusive Barbie line. It features a stylishly dressed Barbie doll with different body types, skin tones.
Meet Grace Thomas, an adventurous and aspiring young baker! Grace comes with beautiful hazel eyes, long dark hair, and a huggable cloth body.

details: Introducing Gabriela McBride, a talented and creative girl who loves expressing herself through poetry and dance! Gabriela has curly dark-brown hair and warm brown eyes.
